&hellip;"},{"pid":"7ae2a3cfaba063e66245a79ea5efcc179b26416f","tid":362482,"uid":137540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:45:53.000Z","msg":"分啦樓主27歲再搵過個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢都唔肯付出 好難落去喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"506e12a3564a19211856e36e804c0bf987274a38","tid":362482,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n我都唔識得講。<br />\n33歲係唔係老男人啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開始步入中年</blockquote><br />\n我都想知道到底男人中年既時候係咪就唔會想扑野，我地半個月先扑一次佢都得嫁wo,上次仲要係我主動先，但佢自己又識得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底咩意思啊&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n樓主幾大?</blockquote><br />\n樓主27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同佢一齊之前都唔知佢係咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始冇咁麻煩啊&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐我可以接受係屋企一齊打ps4就咁就一日，但唔好成日都咁啦，星期日已經唔出街，我唔想星期六又係做屋企做宅癈啊&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n咁你咪自己出街囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做乜要強行逼佢做佢唔想做嘅嘢，仲要佢plan佢唔想做嘅嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb63f2940d76e01ad41fc2c17046b662e6f41384","tid":362482,"uid":134180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:46:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>喺屋企煮吓嘢食睇吓戲訓吓覺囉<br />\n不過男人老狗踩單車都唔識仲要怕曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢係唔識踩單車，但佢其他運動都ok既。<br />\n佢鍾意打羽毛球，咁我話咁我地一齊去打啦，佢就話好難book到場。<br />\n踢足球我就唔識嫁喇。<br />\n唯一一樣就係跑步囉，但我唔太鍾意。<br />\n成日屌鳩我話我懶唔跑，但我就係唔鍾意喘氣個感覺，同埋依個天氣去跑真係會中暑囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁係佢ON9啦</blockquote><br />\n所以我都唔撚識講。<br />\n你話佢係咪冇心啊....<br />\n我同佢一齊都未夠半年啊&hellip;<br />\n成撚日同我講唔洗就佢咁多。<br />\n但屌次次最撚多說話就係佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n典型嘅仆街仔黎, 佢呢種係唔屌唔鬆化, 我諗你要狠狠屌佢一獲金嘅仲好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌過一次啦，上次屌完都未隔一個月，個陣時佢仲仆街到話冷靜下，話我鍾意佢多過佢鍾意我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />跟住話諗下係咪大家需要大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌佢跟住我就上佢屋企到執野兼屌佢一獲金，講到話你唔願意花時間陪我既就不如分開唔好浪漫大家時間。</blockquote><br />\n其實問題係佢唔肯付出</blockquote><br />\n唔夠鍾意我，所以唔想付出咁多囉。<br />\n又唔係叫佢出錢，時間又唔洗錢都唔付出"},{"pid":"c9380fa2078156bd294e6f63b9a3e0329226bd8f","tid":362482,"uid":91047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>咁似老男人行為既？</blockquote><br />\n我都唔識得講。<br />\n33歲係唔係老男人啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開始步入中年</blockquote><br />\n我都想知道到底男人中年既時候係咪就唔會想扑野，我地半個月先扑一次佢都得嫁wo,上次仲要係我主動先，但佢自己又識得打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n到底咩意思啊&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n樓主幾大?</blockquote><br />\n樓主27歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你同佢一齊之前都唔知佢係咁?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一開始冇咁麻煩啊&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐我可以接受係屋企一齊打ps4就咁就一日，但唔好成日都咁啦，星期日已經唔出街，我唔想星期六又係做屋企做宅癈啊&hellip;</blockquote><br />\n唔肯付出嘅男人就唔好比佢浪費你咁多青春啦, 放手啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f064f6b8f6002f3f987400ee7adf88d022fdfde","tid":362482,"uid":134180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T03:51:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><bloc